{"id":232902436,"title":"❗️東海商圈 韓式餐廳 評價驚人","content":"吃餐廳習慣看評價避免踩雷\n相信很多人應該都跟我一樣～\n在東海附近找韓式餐廳\n評價習慣從一星開始看\n才知道不好的地方在哪裡\n才好評估要不要去吃\n\n結果看到這家韓屋的業主回覆也太驚人\n根本撿到槍炮彈藥\n直接嚇壞\n\n\n下圖是我看到的評價 1/5星\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/dcf24c39-7a20-47b9-8e7a-e310302219f0/1280.jpeg\n\n而以下這是業主的回覆\n（有點多分兩張）\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/20ce876d-d7d5-4a99-8ea6-774bab588f04/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/fc56c02c-fd0e-44a8-941f-f31669c9c27f/1280.jpeg\n\n哇嗚這會不會有點反彈太大⋯⋯⋯⋯\n這樣回覆是可以的嗎⋯⋯⋯\n\n還有一些評價也是 1/5星的評論\n（如下）\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/126dcaff-e2d2-4ab8-a249-4249159e681b/1280.jpeg\n然後店主的回覆\n（如下）\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/b480bca2-8ca1-4db4-b760-0ddd74013754/1280.jpeg\n這個還好但我當下看到真的覺得根本對嗆⋯\n嚇到有點不敢去吃了😅","excerpt":"吃餐廳習慣看評價避免踩雷，相信很多人應該都跟我一樣～在東海附近找韓式餐廳，評價習慣從一星開始看，才知道不好的地方在哪裡，才好評估要不要去吃，結果看到這家韓屋的業主回覆也太驚人，根本撿到槍炮彈藥，直接嚇","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"de977130-f3eb-467b-822e-b0e91124e9eb","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-16T13:35:02.751Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-17T11:50:44.611Z","commentCount":22,"likeCount":270,"tags":[],"topics":["東海商圈","韓式","餐廳","評價"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"美食","forumAlias":"food","school":"逢甲大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":257},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":7},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":5},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/dcf24c39-7a20-47b9-8e7a-e310302219f0/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/20ce876d-d7d5-4a99-8ea6-774bab588f04/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/fc56c02c-fd0e-44a8